		<text>Upper Threshold</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_upper_threshold_desc">
		<text>If indoor score (the amount of ray hit) is above this threshold, the effect will be one full value and the custom indoor sound will play</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_lower_threshold">
		<text>Lower Threshold</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_lower_threshold_desc">
		<text>If indoor score (the amount of ray hit) is above this threshold, the reverb affect will start affecting the sound</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_small_preset">
		<text>Small Room Preset</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_small_preset_desc">
		<text>Reverb preset to use in small room</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_small_strength">
		<text>Small Preset Strength</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_small_strength_desc">
		<text>Basically how "reverb" the effect is, 0 is no reverb at all, 1 is the effect will be on full</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_small_length">
		<text>Distance for small preset</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_small_length_desc">
		<text>If the ray hit points distance to the player is smaller than this, small preset will play</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_mid_preset">
		<text>Medium Room Preset</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_mid_preset_desc">
		<text>Reverb preset to use in medium room</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_mid_strength">
		<text>Medium Preset Strength</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_mid_strength_desc">
		<text>Basically how "reverb" the effect is, 0 is no reverb at all, 1 is the effect will be on full</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_mid_length">
		<text>Distance for medium preset</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_mid_length_desc">
		<text>If the ray hit points distance to the player is equal to this, medium preset will play in full</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_large_preset">
		<text>Large Room Preset</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_large_preset_desc">
		<text>Reverb preset to use in large room</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_large_strength">
		<text>Large Preset Strength</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_large_strength_desc">
		<text>Basically how "reverb" the effect is, 0 is no reverb at all, 1 is the effect will be on full</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_large_length">
		<text>Distance for large preset</text>
	</string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_large_length_desc">
		<text>If the ray hit points distance to the player is equal or larger than this, large preset will play in full</text>
	</string>

	<string id="ui_mcm_spatial_audio_sar_main_outdoor_preset">
